'''War Stories''' may refer to:

* ''[[War Stories with Oliver North]]'', a military history program on the Fox News Channel
* ''[[War Stories (2003 film)]]'', a TV movie with Jeff Goldblum
* [[War Stories (Firefly)|"War Stories" (''Firefly'')]], the tenth episode of science-fiction television series ''Firefly''
* ''[[Nambul: War Stories]]'', a manhwa series of the military drama genre written by Hyun Se Lee
* [[War Stories (album)|''War Stories'' (album)]], a 2007 electronic album by UNKLE

